<TD><IMG style="HEIGHT: 99px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; WIDTH: 110px" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/09/20131113/201311131657294877487.png"><BR>着丝点排列在赤道板</TD>
