<TR>
<TD>染色体及DNA数量的变化</TD>
<TD><IMG style="HEIGHT: 148px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; WIDTH: 207px" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/09/20131113/201311131647186219222.png"></TD>
<TD><IMG style="HEIGHT: 153px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; WIDTH: 214px" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/09/20131113/2013111316471941710690.png"></TD></TR>
